# Task Group Definition Policy

When new task groups/tasks are introduced:

1. Define them through `TASK_GROUP_TEMPLATE` and `TASK_TEMPLATE`.
2. Persist definitions in core seed data in the same change set under `backend/app/seed/datasets/core/`.
3. Register core loader wiring under `backend/app/seed/loaders/core/` and `backend/app/seed/__init__.py`.
4. Render via standard TaskBoard flow instead of custom one-off task UIs.

Keep template keys stable and English. Use deterministic due-date offsets.
